data.description: Motivated Seller!! This exquisite newer construction (2019) energy efficient pool home boasts all the bells and whistles to make you feel right at home! Save hundreds a month on your electric bill with the transferable solar panels. Equipped for entertaining, the property features 4 bedrooms (possible 5), 3 bathrooms, and a 3-car garage with a great split floor plan. The kitchen offers an airy and open feel with white cabinets, granite countertops, and stainless-steel appliances. Step outside to enjoy the outdoors and privacy backing to a preserve. The pool features a beach-entry and spa with a heater for year-round enjoyment. The spacious master bedroom offers plenty of space and an extra-large master bathroom with a tub and huge sports shower. No detail was left undone!
